Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 親愛的 你看起來真棒\N{\fs38}Oh, hey, honey. You look sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.58,0:00:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 今天穿上了戰靴啊  - 哦 這雙嗎\N{\fs38}- Got your power heels on. - Oh, these?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.10,0:00:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒啊 就是很普通的\N{\fs38}No, these are just regular
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.02,0:00:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都能買到的樂福鞋\N{\fs38}men's loafers you can buy in any store.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我加了三四個鞋墊 更方便我做這個\N{\fs38}And I put three or four insoles in so it's easier to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 找個房間啦  - 這都是我們的房間\N{\fs38}- Ugh, get a room. - Hey, these are all our rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才該去找個房間 說真的 你怎么穿起正裝了\N{\fs38}You get a room. Seriously, why are you dressed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.90,0:00:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Harris打給我\N{\fs38}Oh, Harris called me in.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說幫我安排了個重要采訪\N{\fs38}He finally set up a big interview for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚我可以問些刁鉆問題了\N{\fs38}Tonight, I get to ask the tough questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.19,0:00:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸你要采訪誰呢\N{\fs38}Who are you interviewing,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.56,0:00:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問 也許我該問的\N{\fs38}Didn't ask. Probably should've.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是個刁鉆問題\N{\fs38}Tough questions start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.74,0:00:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你  - 你這是登岸休假嗎 海員寶貝\N{\fs38}- You... - Are you on shore leave, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在體育館考完游泳后 一打開儲物柜 \N{\fs38}It was swim test day in gym, and when I got back to my locker,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.46,0:00:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面只有這套東西\N{\fs38}this was all that was left in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.29,0:00:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像是高手所為\N{\fs38}Sounds like some smooth criminal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑這天完美作案 收買門衛然后偷走你的運動包\N{\fs38}picked a perfect day to bribe the janitors to swipe your gym bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整蠱成功 你被耍了 \N{\fs38}Sha-boof! You've been pranked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我穿成這樣坐地鐵回來的 丟臉死了\N{\fs38}I had to ride the subway like this. It sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有個老太太說謝謝我的服務\N{\fs38}Although a nice old woman did thank me for my service.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次記住別再吃掉最后一根奶酪棒了\N{\fs38}Next time, don't take the last mozzarella stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我像只野獸一樣在干喝醬料\N{\fs38}I had to drink the sauce like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因為這個嗎 好的\N{\fs38}That's what this is about? Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.13,0:01:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想開戰是吧 奉陪到底\N{\fs38}You want a prank war? You got a prank war!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在玉米花生糖盒子上美極了\N{\fs38}Loved you on the cracker jack box.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.05,0:01:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}爆米花品牌 包裝上有個水手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 瞧我這聰明才智  - 工作找得怎樣了 Ian\N{\fs38}- Upstairs.  - How's the job search going, Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 還沒收到你給的租金  - 馬上就成了\N{\fs38}- Still haven't got that rent check.  - I'm all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我等著我的公司變現的同時\N{\fs38}While I'm waiting for my company to monetize,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在找合適的正職\N{\fs38}I'm searching for the perfect day job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把簡歷放上了鄰客音 就讓那些公司爭破頭吧\N{\fs38}I posted my resume on Linkedin. Let the feeding frenzy begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.98,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}世界上最大的專業網絡社交平臺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.10,0:01:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我個臺階下好嘛\N{\fs38}You gonna help me out with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.73,0:01:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個恩情我會記住的 兄弟\N{\fs38}I won't forget that, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 壞消息\N{\fs38}Guys, bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前很想進的那個作家小組\N{\fs38}That writers' group I've been trying to get into?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 同意我加入了  - 我要說你總會度過這關的嗎\N{\fs38}- They accepted me. - You'll get past this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我每月要招待他們一次\N{\fs38}No, I have to host these guys once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.19,0:01:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不能讓那些出版作家們坐在一張\N{\fs38}I can't have published writers sitting on a couch
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在學校垃圾桶撿回來的破沙發上\N{\fs38}I found in a dumpster in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是從浣熊手中搶過來的啊\N{\fs38}We fought off raccoons for that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.81,0:01:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 若是二十多歲 有張浣熊沙發還說得過去\N{\fs38}Exactly. And while it may be cute to have a raccoon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在我的腳趾已然要邁過三十大關了\N{\fs38}couch in your 20s, I'm dipping my toe into my 30s...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的腳趾有十二年那么長啊  - 我說真的 Michael\N{\fs38}- Your toe is 12 years long? - I'm serious, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個作家組會是我的巨大轉機\N{\fs38}This group could be my big break.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想求你們的 可沙發確實比較貴\N{\fs38}And you know I hate to ask, but couches are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看能不能借我點...\N{\fs38}So maybe you could just loan me a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的文稿經紀人來電話了\N{\fs38}Oh, hey. It's my literary agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 Vernon\N{\fs38}Hey, Vernon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.00,0:02:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總無事不登三寶殿\N{\fs38}Every time she comes up here, she wants something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我總對她有求必應\N{\fs38}And every time she comes up here, I end up giving it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我要打破這個惡性循環\N{\fs38}I gotta break this cycle of dependency.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.66,0:02:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mike 你知道每次對Leigh說"不"都有什么后果嗎\N{\fs38}Mike, you know what happens when you say "No" To Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是小事化大\N{\fs38}The problem just becomes bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得那次你拒絕付錢給她的人生導師嗎\N{\fs38}Remember when you refused to pay for her life coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 那個后來進了康復院的嗎  - 對 她很傷心\N{\fs38}- The one who ended up in rehab? - Yes, she was so upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以至后來你得為她的哀傷心理治療師付錢\N{\fs38}you had to pay for her grief counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個后來自殺的家伙嗎\N{\fs38}The one who killed himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她買沙發吧 Mike\N{\fs38}Just please buy the couch, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.81,0:02:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的經紀人不干了 要去當口腔保健專家\N{\fs38}Well, my agent is leaving me to become a dental hygienist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"他寧愿看別人的口腔\N{\fs38}"He'd rather look at the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不愿看我的文章"\N{\fs38}inside of people's mouths than my writing."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 這是他的原話  - 也許你去還能打折呢\N{\fs38}- That was a quote.  - Maybe you'll get a discount?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我問過了 現在我更急迫的需要這張沙發了\N{\fs38}No, I already asked. Now I need this couch more than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想犧牲多少人呢 Mike\N{\fs38}How many people need to die, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.11,0:02:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沙發包在我們身上  - 就你們最好了\N{\fs38}- We'll get you the couch. - You're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經看上一款了 現在就去買\N{\fs38}I already have one on hold. I'm gonna go get it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 能借把傘嗎\N{\fs38}Oh, hey, can I borrow your umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像要下雨了\N{\fs38}It looks like it's gonna rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是啊 所以我也要用  - Michael 我才做完頭發\N{\fs38}- Yeah, that's why I need it. - Michael, I just did my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿吧\N{\fs38}Take the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:03:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 看吧 多簡單  - 那我用Eve的\N{\fs38}- See, that was easy.  - And I'll just take Eve's umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Henry先生 你全身濕透了\N{\fs38}Mr. Henry, you're soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的病能淋雨嗎\N{\fs38}Can you be in the rain with your condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kay 我只是有帕金森 又不是女巫\N{\fs38}Kay, I have Parkinson's. I'm not a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}女巫 特指綠野仙蹤里被水濺到會融掉的女巫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把健身房毛巾拿來 我不怎么出汗\N{\fs38}I'll get you my gym towel. I barely perspired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說我汗腺小到危及生命的程度\N{\fs38}The doctors say I have dangerously undersized sweat glands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.08,0:03:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就別跑了啊 拜托\N{\fs38}Well, then don't run, for Pete's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 喂  - 好消息 我買了張復古沙發\N{\fs38}- Hello?   - Good news... I got a vintage couch,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以省了點錢 壞消息是\N{\fs38}so I saved us some money. Bad news...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細一看 沙發紋理\N{\fs38}In the cold light of day, the upholstery pattern
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.10,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來像一坨精子\N{\fs38}looks like a bunch of sperms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.76,0:03:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像佩斯利渦旋花紋 不錯啊\N{\fs38}It sounds like paisley. It sounds fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 的確不錯\N{\fs38}No, no, no, no, no. It's totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這個"不錯" 是藥店網的牛仔褲那種"不錯"嗎\N{\fs38}But is it fine like how drugstore jeans are fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}藥店網 主營母嬰用品 保健品的購物網站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如 紐扣把你肚子都壓淤青了\N{\fs38}Like, when the buttons turn your belly green,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口袋都是畫上去的那種不錯嗎\N{\fs38}and the pockets are just drawn on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.47,0:03:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這么想的 翻新一下\N{\fs38}Here's what I'm thinking... we reupholster...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是要花多點錢  - 夠了\N{\fs38}- for just a little more money...   - All right, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh 我很愛你 可你\N{\fs38}Leigh, I love you, but you
