Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 這真是好消息 謝謝了\N{\fs38}Yeah, that's great news. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了 滅蟲的人今天就能來\N{\fs38}Yes. Yes! Exterminator's coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她這周末就能走了 再也不用睡沙發了\N{\fs38}She'll be out at the end of the week. No more couch sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 Mike 真是不錯 真是不錯\N{\fs38}Yeah, Mike. That's great, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你在鏡頭里\N{\fs38}But you're in the shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一邊指著這些注釋\N{\fs38}If you could just point at these notes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 一邊慢慢走開 - 快點\N{\fs38}- while we walk away... - Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我太高興了 只是剛剛知道苦日子要結束了\N{\fs38}Sorry, I'm in a good mood. Just knowing the end is near
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 感覺一切都沒那么難以忍受了 - 是啊\N{\fs38}- makes it all seem bearable. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就跟平胸女人調情一樣\N{\fs38}Like going to a play with a flat-chested woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這兒 看看她對我的襪子做了什么\N{\fs38}Look at this. Look what she does to my socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她穿了我的襪子 用她那巨腳丫子把我襪子都撐變形了\N{\fs38}She puts them on her big, giant feet and she stretches them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看這火雞都這樣了 你看看\N{\fs38}Look at this turkey gobble. Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么多松松垮垮的地方\N{\fs38}Yeah, so much saggy material.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是平胸女人的襯衣一樣\N{\fs38}Like a blouse on a flat-chested woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚的約會咋樣了\N{\fs38}How'd your date go last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還行吧 嗨 聽好了\N{\fs38}The play was all right. Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我找了個正經采訪\N{\fs38}I got a real interview this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天你跟克里斯·克里斯帝面對面專訪\N{\fs38}Tomorrow you're going toe-to-toe with Chris Christie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}新澤西州州長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 真的嗎 - 是的\N{\fs38}- No, really? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 真是太棒了 - 是啊\N{\fs38}- That's fantastic! - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得好好準備下 - 好的\N{\fs38}- I gotta go prepare. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到頭來成專訪穿風衣的貓\N{\fs38}If this turns out to be a cat in a windbreaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我會殺了你 - Mike 你在鏡頭里\N{\fs38}- I'm gonna murder you. - Mike, you're in the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡覺的時候你吐我床上了\N{\fs38}You're throwing in my bed while I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 噢 - 好了 別再看壞女孩俱樂部了\N{\fs38}- Oh! - Okay, enough bad girls club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在客廳工作了\N{\fs38}I'm gonna be working in the dining room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要準備一個重要專訪...\N{\fs38}I gotta prepare my big interview with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.34,0:10:07.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 Cheyenne正說話呢\N{\fs38}Shh! Cheyenne is talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 Leigh讓你跟著一起看這個了嗎\N{\fs38}What, has Aunt Leigh got you watching this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是還有論文要寫嗎\N{\fs38}Don't you have a paper to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的假發落在告解室了\N{\fs38}Her weave is in the confessional.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 她剛剛是不是把頭發拿下來了\N{\fs38}Wait a minute, did she just take her hair off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是丑斃的假發而已 老爸\N{\fs38}It's just a busted-ass weave, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- "孔雀裝逼"開始了 - "孔雀裝逼"啥意思\N{\fs38}- Let the peacocking begin. - What the hell is "Peacocking"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你給高檔西服上配上浮夸的配件\N{\fs38}It's when you add a flashy accessory to an upscale suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是工作面試時候活絡話題的法寶\N{\fs38}It's an instant conversation starter at a job interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 容我先說一說\N{\fs38}Well, let me start a conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你買西服哪兒來的錢\N{\fs38}Where'd you get the money to buy the suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.02,0:10:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把奶奶給我的儲蓄債券兌現了\N{\fs38}Oh, I cashed in the savings bond Grandma gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是罰了一點款 是因為還沒到期\N{\fs38}There was a penalty because it hadn't matured.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得時機已到 謝謝你的建議 Leigh姑姑\N{\fs38}But I have. Thanks for the advice, Aunt Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想脫穎而出 著裝就得先脫穎而出啊\N{\fs38}If you want to stand out in business, you have to look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.66,0:10:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須先花了錢 才能去掙錢\N{\fs38}You gotta spend money to make money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.30,0:10:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 必須先掙了錢 才有錢去花\N{\fs38}No. No, see, you have to make money to spend money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔雀叫著 要飛走了\N{\fs38}That's a peacock sound. Gotta fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孔雀可不會飛\N{\fs38}Peacocks don't fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.58,0:10:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 老爸 你看見我ipod沒\N{\fs38}Hey, Dad. Have you seen my iPod?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.12,0:10:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇擦 伙計 你這是干嘛\N{\fs38}Whoa, buddy. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱可不允許在家里裸奔\N{\fs38}We don't walk around the house naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 今天早上我看到Leigh姑姑\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah, we do. I saw Aunt Leigh this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廚房里光著身子喝橙汁呢\N{\fs38}chugging orange juice in the kitchen naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.78,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別搞笑了\N{\fs38}Turn it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh開始掌控這個家了 我有兩個選擇\N{\fs38}Leigh had taken over the house. I had two options...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直面這個問題或者\N{\fs38}Confront the problem directly or...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在這兒準備克里斯蒂的專訪嗎\N{\fs38}This is where you're prepping for your Christie interview?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在這兒能靜下心來 要是我餓了\N{\fs38}Yeah, it's easier to focus in here, and if I get hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 百花包里還有酸果蔓 - 我明白了\N{\fs38}- there's dried cranberry in the potpourri. - I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更輕松的辦法是你直接付了Leigh翻新沙發的錢\N{\fs38}A lazy mind might think that it would've been easier
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒這么多事兒了\N{\fs38}for you to just buy Leigh that upholstery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有什么教育意義呢\N{\fs38}Where would the lesson be in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已經打破這個惡性循環了 - 是的 是的 \N{\fs38}- I've broken the cycle, honey. - Yes. Yes, you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就只是犧牲了幾晚上睡沙發\N{\fs38}And all it cost me was a couple nights on a sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上特早起來和在廁所辦公\N{\fs38}and getting up extra early and working in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有在衣籃上打字 天 求你了 寶貝\N{\fs38}and typing on a hamper... oh, god, please, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得幫幫我 快擺脫掉她\N{\fs38}You gotta help me. You gotta get rid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 好吧 我今晚把她帶出去\N{\fs38}Okay, okay, okay. Um... I'll take her out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.76,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她喝點酒 把她軟化然后\N{\fs38}I will soften her up with a few drinks and then
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.48,0:11:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在慢慢的建議她 趕緊麻溜的閃人\N{\fs38}I will gently suggest that she get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有句話得說明白 這些我提前都猜到了\N{\fs38}But just for the record, I predicted all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 連廁所都猜到了 - 不 這個算是額外驚喜\N{\fs38}- Even the toilet? - No, that was just a fun bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fonz的辦公室也是在廁所的\N{\fs38}Just so you know, the Fonz's office was in a bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}電視連續劇中角色 他把附近一家漢堡包連鎖店的男廁所當作自己的辦公室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 寶貝 你跟Fonz差遠了 - 嗨\N{\fs38}- Honey, you are so not the Fonz. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.49,0:12:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整蠱Ian太容易了 因為他太過自信\N{\fs38}It's easy to prank Ian because he's so sure of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是出錯 卻從不懷疑\N{\fs38}Often wrong, never in doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.46,0:12:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃是讓他最終放棄無奈的向服務員要賬單\N{\fs38}The plan was for him to eventually give up and ask for the check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.65,0:12:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我叫服務員拿給他\N{\fs38}Then I'd have the waitress bring him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個奶酪棒和一頂水手帽\N{\fs38}a single mozzarella stick and a sailor cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.28,0:12:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整蠱成功\N{\fs38}Sha-boof.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以為這會很有趣\N{\fs38}It was supposed to be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是并沒有\N{\fs38}But it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓 Mike明天有個很重要的采訪\N{\fs38}Shh. Mike has a very big interview tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道怎么溜進漆黑的房間里\N{\fs38}I think I know how to sneak into a dark apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.05,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這東西什么時候在那兒的\N{\fs38}Oh, that came out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 嗨 - 現在可是凌晨兩點了\N{\fs38}- Hi. - It's 2:00 in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便了 Mike大本鐘\N{\fs38}Whatever, Mike o'Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.12,0:13:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這確實搞笑 因為你不是愛爾蘭人\N{\fs38}Okay, that... that is funny because you are not Irish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啥 - 還有我們都喝多了\N{\fs38}- Huh? - Also 'cause we're drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我們一接吻\N{\fs38}The bartender gave us
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.31,0:13:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒保就請我們喝酒\N{\fs38}free drinks every time we kissed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下好了 你喚醒了"大學Annie"\N{\fs38}Oh, great, you reawakened "College Annie."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 大學Annie會伸舌頭的\N{\fs38}Oh, no. "College Annie" Would've used tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我會的 - 我老婆跟我妹接吻\N{\fs38}- I would have. - My wife is kissing my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是 真是好玩 你知道還有啥好玩不\N{\fs38}That's... that's fun. You know what else is fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立馬上床睡覺 我必須得睡覺了\N{\fs38}Going to bed immediately. I've got to get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你確定一定以及肯定是對的\N{\fs38}You are absolutely, totally right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就去\N{\fs38}And we are gonna pull it together for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 比薩 比薩到了  - 噢\N{\fs38}- Pizza! Pizza! - Oh, pucker up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要免費的長棍面包\N{\fs38}I want free crazy bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不行 別親了  - 嗨 比薩小子\N{\fs38}- No! No kissing for bread! - Hey, Mr. Pizza man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底死哪去了 還有五分鐘就開始了\N{\fs38}Where the hell have you been? We're on in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣色不錯 Henry先生 我不能騙你\N{\fs38}Looking good, Mr. Henry. I can't lie to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來像在溝里過了一夜\N{\fs38}You look like you slept in a ditch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我沒睡好 我妹妹親了我老婆\N{\fs38}I didn't get much sleep last night. My sister kissed my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙發上把面包吐得到處都是\N{\fs38}and then threw up crazy bread all over the couch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.17,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你辦了派對卻沒邀請我\N{\fs38}Oh, so you had a party and didn't invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.90,0:14:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 我們去吧\N{\fs38}Let's go, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不不不  - 這邊\N{\fs38}- Oh! No, no, no, no. - Okay, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這邊 攝影機和燈光都在那邊\N{\fs38}he's over here where all the cameras and the lights are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 早上好 州長先生  - Mike 幸會\N{\fs38}- Hello, Governor. - Mike, great to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝你們請我來  - 我的榮幸\N{\fs38}- Thanks for having me on. - My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 很好  - 你握得太用力了\N{\fs38}- Great. - You're crushing my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉  - 大家好 我是Mike Henry\N{\fs38}- Oh, sorry. - Hello, I'm Mike Henry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們將對話新澤西州長\N{\fs38}Today we'll be speaking to the Governor of New Jersey,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.62,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯·克里斯帝先生\N{\fs38}Chris Christie. Governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 歡迎你  - 謝謝你 Mike \N{\fs38}- welcome. - Mike, thanks for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.32,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興看到你重返崗位\N{\fs38}I'm so glad to see you back doing your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 我認為你的經歷非常激勵人\N{\fs38}And, you know, I find your story just so inspiring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上 我認為你是勵志的楷模\N{\fs38}in fact, I think it's so inspiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會上有許多傳聞\N{\fs38}There's been a lot of speculation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天受到你的鼓舞\N{\fs38}about things, and I feel so inspired today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.37,0:14:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做一個公開說明 那么 Mike\N{\fs38}I think I should make an announcement. So Mike...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫醒他\N{\fs38}Wake him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fs38}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松餅\N{\fs38}Muffins!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.29,0:14:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等等再討論這個問題\N{\fs38}Uh... Well, we'll get to that question later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:14:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我何必費這個心呢\N{\fs38}Why do I even bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 哦  - 某人喝瘋了哈\N{\fs38}- Oh... - Someone's got a hangover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是派對和快樂時光過后的惡心頭痛而已\N{\fs38}No, just a little party headache with some good-time nausea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.39,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你在做什么  - 給我和Ian煎蛋\N{\fs38}- What are you doing? - Making omelets for me and Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 真體貼\N{\fs38}Oh, that's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你爸爸和你姑姑也這么友愛\N{\fs38}I wish your father and your aunt were as close as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.83,0:15:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 這個長棍面包哪來的\N{\fs38}Hey, where'd this crazy bread come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你真不記得了  - 我現在正需要它\N{\fs38}- You seriously don't remember? - This is exactly what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.77,0:15:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是...不 不 再等等\N{\fs38}I just... oh, god, no. Whoa, too soon. Too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 來個煎蛋嗎  - 你剛坐在上面了吧\N{\fs38}- Want an omelet? - You probably put your butt on them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.23,0:15:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對屁股味的煎蛋不太感興趣 還是算了吧\N{\fs38}and since I'm not partial to butt omelets, I shall pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來心情不錯啊\N{\fs38}You seem to be in a good mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Johnson昨晚沒出現\N{\fs38}Johnson was actually a no-show last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他發了郵件來道歉\N{\fs38}but I got an email from him apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能對他太殘忍\N{\fs38}I had to let him down easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說如果不是昨天搬到波基普西去了的話\N{\fs38}He said I'd have been an Insta-hire
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會果斷錄用我\N{\fs38}if they'd not just relocated to Poughkeepsie last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許這樣最好\N{\fs38}Well, maybe it's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以我要去波基普西  - 等等 什么\N{\fs38}- So I'm going to Poughkeepsie. - Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我要去趕火車了\N{\fs38}Now if you'll excuse me, I have a train to catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 Ian\N{\fs38}Wait... Ian?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh 我們一定要 天哪這是什么\N{\fs38}Leigh, we have to ta... Oh, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼管舞\N{\fs38}Pole dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.00,0:16:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以激發潛能 而且對脊柱也很有好處\N{\fs38}It's so empowering, and it's really good for your core.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么 算了\N{\fs38}How did you... nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我在早上一整個重要的采訪中 都昏昏欲睡\N{\fs38}Look, I fell asleep during my big interview with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉下剪式\N{\fs38}Scissor grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我能感受到身體在燃燒 Mike  - 去樓下燒吧\N{\fs38}- I can really feel the burn, Mike. - Take the burn downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然驅蟲的人走了 你可以回去了\N{\fs38}It should be aired out now the exterminator's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.97,0:16:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙來過 但他沒噴藥\N{\fs38}Oh, the exterminator came, but he didn't spray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他沒什么  - 他告訴我藥劑有毒的時候\N{\fs38}- He didn't what?! - When he told me how
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就讓他哪來回哪去了\N{\fs38}toxic that stuff was, I sent him on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望有一種毒藥\N{\fs38}Hopefully to get an even deadlier chemical
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓你快點離開這里\N{\fs38}that will get you out of here faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.42,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 我的營養師說 要燒鼠尾草\N{\fs38}Don't worry. My nutritionist said to burn sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常需要兩到三星期\N{\fs38}It usually takes about two to three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"兩到三星期" 還是你的營養師說的\N{\fs38}"Two to three weeks"? And this time line is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真是 毫無意義\N{\fs38}from your nutritionist, so it means... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.71,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 Mike 臭蟲又不是在你床上\N{\fs38}Calm down, Mike. You'd think you were the one with bed bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它確實在 Leigh 就是你\N{\fs38}I do have bed bugs, Leigh. You're my bed bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闖進我家里 擾亂我的家人 毀了我的生活\N{\fs38}You've infested my house, you've destroyed our lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你 現在就給我走\N{\fs38}I've gotta get you out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是唯一一個你沒有放乳液的地方\N{\fs38}That's the only thing in this house you haven't put lotion on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 我自己來搞定\N{\fs38}That's it. I'm doing it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么  - 那個驅蟲的家伙手上有活\N{\fs38}- What? - The exterminator was booked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我給了他一百塊 他給了我殺蟲劑\N{\fs38}So I slipped him 100 bucks. He gave me the pesticides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氧氣罐有了 噴霧器有了\N{\fs38}I got bombs, I got sprays,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放汽車電池里那玩意也有了\N{\fs38}I got the stuff they put in car batteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs36}硫酸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然還在床上躺著啊\N{\fs38}Are you seriously still in bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你拒絕Leigh的下場\N{\fs38}This is what happens when you say "No" To Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是和Leigh一起灌酒的下場吧\N{\fs38}This is what happens when you drink Jager shots with Leigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.17,0:17:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的保護措施\N{\fs38}That's all the protection you're using?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大腦都損傷了 一點點化學藥劑能奈我何\N{\fs38}I got a brain disease. What are a few chemicals gonna do to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.66,0:17:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}Ian Ian\NIan! Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.81,0:17:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Ian  - Eve 你來這做什么\N{\fs38}- Ian! - Eve, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒David Johnson這人 是我編的\N{\fs38}There is no David Johnson. I made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了報復你\N{\fs38}This was my prank to get you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒想過會變成這樣\N{\fs38}I-I never meant for it to get this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.52,0:17:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺糟透了\N{\fs38}I feel terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了吧\N{\fs38}Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往波基普西的19次列車即將開啟\N{\fs38}All aboard track 19 for Poughkeepsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得走了 下次再見\N{\fs38}Gotta run. See you when I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著Ian 我不再感到愧疚了\N{\fs38}Watching Ian, I didn't feel bad anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始嫉妒他\N{\fs38}I was actually jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也許還沒想好未來的事 但一旦他想清楚了\N{\fs38}He might not have it all figured out, but once he does,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒有什么能夠阻擋他\N{\fs38}there is absolutely nothing that'll stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,300)}{\fs36}柏金森疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會讓你的臉年輕十歲\N{\fs38}This will take ten years off your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我才八歲呢\N{\fs38}But I'm only eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh姑姑在給我們敷泥面膜 你想來嗎\N{\fs38}Aunt Leigh is making us all mud masks. You want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不是還有論文要寫嗎  - 寫完了\N{\fs38}- Don't you still have a paper to write? - I finished it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整整八頁 關于真人秀的上癮問題\N{\fs38}Eight pages on the addictive qualities of reality TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從來沒這么高效過\N{\fs38}I've never been more productive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為獎勵是繼續看<壞女孩俱樂部>\N{\fs38}because my reward was more bad girls club.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來知識本身不是獎勵\N{\fs38}I guess knowledge isn't its own reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"孔雀裝逼裝"得到了回報\N{\fs38}So the peacocking paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時我在去波基普西的火車上\N{\fs38}I was on the train to Poughkeepsie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 說來話長  - 那就跳過\N{\fs38}- long story... - Don't need to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.81,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個家伙說他喜歡我的穿衣風格\N{\fs38}When this guy said he liked my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來他是<今日男士>的職員\N{\fs38}Turns out he works for Today's Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我稍稍施展魅力 砰 工作搞定\N{\fs38}So I turned up the charm, and sha-dank! Job offer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.49,0:19:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 銷售合伙人  - 所以你現在是個西裝銷售員了\N{\fs38}- sales associate. - So you're a suit salesman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是西裝贈送員\N{\fs38}No, I'm a suit givesman
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.06,0:19:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們基本上是白送 砰\N{\fs38}because we're basically just giving them away. Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個月的月租\N{\fs38}First month's rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你這是你的功勞\N{\fs38}Wow. I suppose you had something to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這都是他自己的能耐\N{\fs38}No, he did this all on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 也許Leigh總是無事不登三寶殿\N{\fs38}Sure, maybe Leigh only comes up here when she wants something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.97,0:19:55.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有時候她想要的不過是\N{\fs38}But sometimes that something...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她的家人待在一起而已\N{\fs38}is just to be around her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 我知道我一直招你嫌\N{\fs38}Hey, listen, I know I've been a giant pain in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我會趕緊把房子弄清楚 不來煩你了\N{\fs38}So I'm just gonna get cleaned up, and I'll be out of your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leigh 為啥會刺痛啊\N{\fs38}Leigh, are these supposed to tingle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.59,0:20:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就說明辣椒有用啊\N{\fs38}That's how you know the cayenne pepper's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想是不是沒人知道里邊還有辣椒啊\N{\fs38}I'm guessing no one knew about the cayenne pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很好 就像把臉塞在螞蟻窩里一樣爽\N{\fs38}It's great. It's like sticking your face in an anthill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快點 把這個洗掉\N{\fs38}Okay, let's go, guys. Let's take these off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不能敷到一半就\N{\fs38}People, you can't jump midstream. It'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 啊  - 天哪 弄到鼻子里了\N{\fs38}- Aah! - Oh, god, it's up my nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我鼻子里 在我鼻子里\N{\fs38}It's in my nose! It's in my nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很適合你的形象\N{\fs38}That's a good look for you.
